author: The Critical Drinker
description: Multimillion dollar lawsuits, destroyed careers, public feuds and a web of lies and smear campaigns. This movie has it all, igniting one of the most bitter public battles in Hollywood history between Justin Baldoni and Blake Lively, Ryan Reynolds and even Taylor Swift. But how did we even get here? Well, let's find out.
title: Production Hell - It Ends With Us
